graphql.query:
mutation ($payload:CciCreateJobDetailInput!)
{
	cciCreateJobDetail (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		executionType
		executionExecutedAt
		executionMonitoringStartAt
		executionMonitoringEndAt
		status
		name
		returnCode
		node
		user
		startAt
		endAt
	}
}

query ($query:QueryStatement)
{
	cciGetJobsDetail (query: $query)
	{
		id
		tenantCode
		systemName
		executionType
		executionExecutedAt
		executionMonitoringStartAt
		executionMonitoringEndAt
		status
		name
		returnCode
		node
		user
		startAt
		endAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
